# 🏗️ ConsistencyGrid — Premium Subscription Architecture

> Complete technical blueprint for website + Android WebView premium subscription system with Razorpay, Play Store compliance, and production-grade security.

---

## 📐 Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Client Layer"
        WEB["🌐 Website (Next.js)<br/>Full Payment UI"]
        ANDROID["📱 Android WebView<br/>No Payment UI"]
    end

    subgraph "Edge Layer"
        MW["🛡️ Next.js Middleware<br/>JWT · CSP · Security Headers<br/>Platform Detection"]
    end

    subgraph "API Layer"
        AUTH_API["🔐 Auth APIs<br/>signup · login · session<br/>webview-login · native-auth"]
        PAY_API["💳 Payment APIs<br/>create-order · verify<br/>plans · subscription"]
        WEBHOOK["🔔 Webhook Endpoint<br/>/api/payment/webhook<br/>(No Auth Required)"]
        FEATURE_API["⚡ Feature APIs<br/>habits · goals · reminders<br/>analytics · settings"]
    end

    subgraph "Business Logic"
        SUB_MW["📋 Subscription Middleware<br/>checkHabitLimit<br/>checkGoalLimit<br/>checkFeatureAccess"]
        PLAT["🔍 Platform Utils<br/>isAndroidApp()<br/>shouldShowPaymentUI()<br/>getPlatformMessages()"]
        SUB_UTIL["🔧 Subscription Utils<br/>canAddHabit · canAddGoal<br/>getFeatureAccess<br/>hasActiveSubscription"]
    end

    subgraph "Payment Providers"
        RP["🟢 Razorpay Provider<br/>createOrder · verifyPayment<br/>verifyWebhook · createRefund"]
        SP["🔵 Stripe Provider<br/>(backup / international)"]
    end

    subgraph "Data Layer"
        DB[("🐘 PostgreSQL<br/>Prisma ORM")]
