    end

    subgraph "External Services"
        RPay["Razorpay API"]
        EMAIL["📧 Resend (Email)"]
        SENTRY["🐛 Sentry (Monitoring)"]
    end

    WEB --> MW --> AUTH_API & PAY_API & FEATURE_API
    ANDROID --> MW --> AUTH_API & FEATURE_API
    
    PAY_API --> RP & SP
    WEBHOOK --> RP
    
    RP --> RPay
    
    AUTH_API & PAY_API & FEATURE_API --> SUB_MW --> DB
    SUB_MW --> SUB_UTIL
    WEB --> PLAT
    ANDROID --> PLAT
    
    FEATURE_API --> CACHE
    PAY_API --> EMAIL
    WEBHOOK --> EMAIL
    PAY_API & WEBHOOK --> SENTRY
```

