## 4️⃣ Android WebView Compatibility

### 4.1 Platform Detection System

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["Page Loads"] --> B["isAndroidApp()"]
    B --> C{"User-Agent check"}
    C -->|"Contains 'webview' or 'wv'"| YES["✅ Android"]
    C -->|No| D{"window.Android exists?"}
    D -->|Yes| YES
    D -->|No| E{"localStorage flag?"}
    E -->|"'consistencygrid_platform' === 'android'"| YES
    E -->|No| NO["❌ Web Browser"]
    
    YES --> HIDE["Hide Payment UI<br/>Show 'Continue on Website'"]
    NO --> SHOW["Show Full Payment UI"]
```

### 4.2 Your Platform Utils (Already Implemented)

From [platform-utils.js](file:///d:/startup/consistencygrid/src/lib/platform-utils.js):

```javascript
// Three-layer Android detection:
export function isAndroidApp() {
    // 1. User-Agent analysis
    const isWebView = /webview|wv|android.*applewebkit(?!.*chrome)/i.test(userAgent);
    
    // 2. Custom Android interface (injected from Kotlin)
    const hasAndroidInterface = typeof window.Android !== 'undefined';
    
    // 3. localStorage flag (set on first load by Android)
    const hasAppFlag = localStorage.getItem('consistencygrid_platform') === 'android';
    
    return isWebView || hasAndroidInterface || hasAppFlag;
}

// Control what's shown:
export function shouldShowPaymentUI()  { return !isAndroidApp(); }
export function getUpgradeUrl()        { return isAndroidApp() ? externalUrl : '/pricing'; }
export function getPlatformMessages()  { /* Different button text */ }
```

### 4.3 Android Middleware Bypass

From [middleware.js](file:///d:/startup/consistencygrid/middleware.js):

```javascript
// Detect native Android app
const isNativeAndroid = userAgent.includes('ConsistencyGridApp') 
                     || req.cookies.has('native_auth');

// Android native users bypass NextAuth JWT check
// (they use publicToken-based auth instead)
if (isNativeAndroid && isProtectedRoute) {
    return NextResponse.next();
}
```

### 4.4 Authentication Token Flow in WebView

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Android App (Kotlin)
    participant W as WebView
    participant API as Backend

    A->>API: POST /api/native-auth/email-login {email, password}
    API-->>A: {publicToken, user}
    A->>W: Set cookie: publicToken=xxx
    A->>W: Set cookie: native_auth=true
    A->>W: Set localStorage: consistencygrid_platform=android
    W->>API: Any API call (cookie sent automatically)
    API->>API: getUniversalSession() reads publicToken
    API-->>W: Response with user data
```

